messageBody:
ashu_2001 wrote:

> In my TestClass i have written the proper setUp() method and it is not
> getting called-anyone knowing what's happening here?

Not without code, we don't.

> What's the execution order of junit's methods?

Look at the source for details.

instantiate test case
setUp
runTest
tearDown

If your setUp() method is not invoked, then you have done something
wrong. If you show us your TestCase source code, we will probably see
the problem.
